articles.author: KEN MORITSUGU Associated Press
articles.title: The Year of the Snake is underway with Lunar New Year festivities around the world - ABC News
articles.description: Firecrackers, parades and prayers marked the Lunar New Year as millions around Asia and farther afield celebrated
articles.content:
BEIJING -- Firecrackers popped, incense was offered at temples and dancers and drummers paraded Wednesday in Asia and farther afield as millions around the world celebrated the Lunar New Year.
